{
  "stem": "3933.4",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we need additional hours in the night.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We'll wake you up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Never mind the baby.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We have German women in our country.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We work nights.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It's a war.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he started to pick on me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he suspected I'm Jewish.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he said-- I'll never forget this-- girls, look what he made a gesture.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Look, Joan-- that's the gesture he made.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You're going to be locked up.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "In these two hands he made the gesture.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I can't forget it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "You're going to be locked up.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Oh, you're going to be first in jail, makes a gesture like I'm going to be cross-crossed in a jail.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I said to myself, OK, it's short time, and it's maybe the end-- maybe it's not, because you keep listening to the news.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They are getting farther and father.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They-- now with America joining in, and England, and France.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "You know these stories.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I, please I want to survive.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And finally, I left this place, and I went to another place.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "The [NON-ENGLISH] in the streets-- the [NON-ENGLISH], megaphones, something, keep telling this front is coming down, down.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And finally, the Russians, the paratroopers came in.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And I couldn't believe it, God.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And I do speak Russian.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I just couldn't believe it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I just wanted to jump.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I want to say, when I was in Warsaw-- going back for a minute-- I was riding this tram when was in  Warsaw, going to work, functioning, and we ride down the ghetto-- it was shortly after the end of the Warsaw Ghetto.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "When I looked through there, and I see the windows, you can see because it's a very high parka-- a-- a wall, a wall.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "But when you are high, you can see the windows open from the buildings.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
